							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/lincoln-michel/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Lincoln-Michel-by-Adalena-Kavanagh-100x100.jpg" width="100" height="100" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Lincoln-Michel-by-Adalena-Kavanagh-300x300.jpg 2x" alt="Lincoln Michel" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/lincoln-michel/">Lincoln Michel</a></h6>
										Lincoln Michel’s most recent novel is <em>Metallic Realms</em> (Atria Books). His previous books include the story collection <em>Upright Beasts</em> (Coffee House Press) and the novel <em>The Body Scout</em> (Orbit), which was named one of the fifty best science fiction of all time by <em>Esquire</em>. His fiction appears in <em>The Paris Review</em>, <em>Strange Horizons</em>, <em>F&SF</em>, <em>Granta</em>, and <em>McSweeney’s</em>. You can find him online at lincolnmichel.com and his newsletter <em>Counter Craft</em>.																				<div class="website">
			    							<i class="fa fa-link"></i>
				    						<a href="http://lincolnmichel.com" target="_blank" class="external">http://lincolnmichel.com</a>
				    					</div>
				    														</div>
								</div><br class="clear"/><br/>
							</div>
							<br class="clear"/>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div>
													<div class="sidebar_content ad_bottom">
								<li id="custom_ads-24" class="widget Custom_Ads"><div class="htlad-LH_PP_F"></div></li>
							</div>
												<div class="post_wrapper" style="padding-top:0">
							<div class="post_wrapper_inner">
								
															</div>
						</div>
